{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SnowplowTracker\/documentation\/SnowplowTracker","doc:\/\/SnowplowTracker\/documentation\/SnowplowTracker\/Snowplow"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/snowplowtracker\/snowplow\/refresh(onsuccess:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Reconfigure, create or delete the trackers based on the configuration downloaded remotely."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"refresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"onSuccess"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" ([","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":"]?, ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SnowplowTracker\/documentation\/SnowplowTracker\/ConfigurationState","text":"ConfigurationState","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@SnowplowTracker@E@SPConfigurationState"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"onSuccess","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The callback called when a configuration (cached or downloaded) is set It passes the list of the namespaces associated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the created trackers."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The trackers configuration is automatically download from the endpoint indicated in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"RemoteConfiguration","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"previously used to setup the trackers.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method is asynchronous and you can receive the list of the created trackers in the callbacks once the trackers are created."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The downloaded configuration updates the cached one only if the configuration version is greater than the cached one."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Otherwise the cached one is kept and the callback is not called."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"IMPORTANT: The EventStore will persist all the events that have been tracked but not yet sent.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Those events are attached to the namespace.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If the tracker is removed or the app relaunched with a different namespace, those events can’t","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be sent to the collector and they remain in a zombie state inside the EventStore.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"To remove all the zombie events you can call an internal method ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"removeUnsentEventsExceptForNamespaces"},{"text":" on ","type":"text"},{"code":"SPSQLEventStore","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which will delete all the EventStores instanced with namespaces not listed in the passed list."}]}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:@M@SnowplowTracker@objc(cs)SPSnowplow(cm)refreshOnSuccess:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"refresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"onSuccess"},{"kind":"text","text":": (["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"St